places.name: Grand Mosque of Conakry
places.perex: The Conakry Grand Mosque is a mosque in Conakry, Guinea, located east of the Conakry Botanical Garden and beside the Donka Hospital.

places.name: Tinkisso Falls
places.perex: Tinkisso Falls is a waterfall on the Tinkisso River located near Dabola in central Guinea. The falls are 70 m wide and 45 m high.

places.name: Sandervalia National Museum
places.perex: The Sandervalia National Museum is the national museum of Guinea, situated in the capital, Conakry.

places.name: St. Mary's Cathedral, Conakry
places.perex: The Cathédrale Sainte-Marie is an important place of Christian worship in Conakry, Guinea.

places.name: Kissidougou Airport
places.perex: Kissidougou Airport is an airport serving Kissidougou in Guinea.

places.name: Garafiri Dam
places.perex: The Garafiri Dam is an embankment dam on the Konkouré River which forms the boundary between the Kindia and Mamou Regions of Guinea.

places.name: Banieya Dam
places.perex: The Banieya Dam is an embankment dam on the Samou River in the Kindia Region of Guinea. It is located 16 km west of Kindia.

places.name: Clinique Ambroise Paré
places.perex: The Clinique Ambroise Paré is a hospital in Conakry, Guinea, is considered to be the best hospital in the country.
